It also touches upon logic programming (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL) in its discussion of Lifschitz's two-valued logic programs. The paper also discusses the functional stable model semantics, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and decision systems engineering (cs.DS).
